# Jarvis – Private AI Workspace

Jarvis is a local, privacy-first AI assistant designed for internal knowledge, support workflows, and document-based intelligence.

Built to run entirely on-premise with GPU acceleration.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🔒 100% local AI (no cloud dependency)
- 📚 RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) with your own documents
- ⚡ Fast response with optimized models (Mistral, Qwen)
- 🧠 Multi-model support via Ollama
- 📄 Supports PDF, DOCX, XLSX, CSV, TXT, MD
- 🏢 Designed for internal knowledge bases (CICS, support docs, etc.)

---

## 🧠 How it works

1. Documents are ingested into a vector database (ChromaDB)
2. Text is chunked and embedded
3. Queries retrieve relevant context
4. LLM (via Ollama) generates answers based on your data

---

## ⚙️ Setup

```bash
git clone https://github.com/alexmarculescu/jarvis.git
cd jarvis

python3 -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate

pip install -r requirements.txt
